    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_09_03/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_sad-04.m4a",
      "text": "退屈だな～、こういう時はボードゲームをやりたいな～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.066666619,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_09_03/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_think-06.m4a",
      "text": "でも一人じゃ遊べないんだよね～。……ちらっ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.3264262937,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_09_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "変なアピールはやめてくれ。気が散って仕事に集中……\n……こんなやり取り、前にもした気がするな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.1333334366,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_09_03/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_angry-03.m4a",
      "text": "冷たいな～\nいいもん、構ってくれないなら一人で遊ぶから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.3666665156,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_09_03/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_sad-05.m4a",
      "text": "……と言っても、幽霊が一人で出来る遊びなんて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.3521760781,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "限られてるんだよね。何をしようかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.4223382565,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "一人で出来ること……うーん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.8629021485,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_09_03/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_think-05.m4a",
      "text": "そうだ！　カラオケしよう！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.9000041722,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_09_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（あ、この曲は……。なんだか思い出すな）\n（この曲が完成した時、俺が聴いてみたいと言ったら）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.2000054436,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "office-00-000-noon",
      "startTime": 52.9869632878
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_09_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_02-mna001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}くんにも\n本番まで聴かせてあげない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.8666654984,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "office-00-000-night",
      "startTime": 58.0843602019
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_09_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "（そう言って、俺の前では歌ってくれなかったのに）\n（今になって麻奈の声で聞けるなんて……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.8333408115,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_09_03/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_ask-09.m4a",
      "text": "あれ～？　{user}くん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.7091222284,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "手が止まってるよ？　仕事しなくていいの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.0670538505,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_09_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "し、仕方ないだろ。あの時聴けなかった曲を\n目の前で長瀬麻奈が歌っているんだぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.5714963776,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_09_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "そんなの、聴き入るに決まってるじゃないか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.8807152269,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_09_03/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_manename-02.m4a",
      "text": "{user}くんは",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.5743886469,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_09_03/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_glad-04.m4a",
      "text": "私の歌、大好きだもんね～。素直でよろしい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.5776793507,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "でも、喜んでくれるのは嬉しいけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.3184464929,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_09_03/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_sad-01.m4a",
      "text": "君にしか歌声が聞こえないのはちょっと寂しいね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.4081322865,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "もっと沢山の人に聴いてほしいなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.4091731863,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ステージが恋しいよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.8296553117,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_09_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "『song for you』……やっぱり\n決勝で歌えなかったことは今でも心残りなのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.0000176506,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_09_03/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_no-02.m4a",
      "text": "それは違うよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.9532380578,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "未練があるとしたら決勝で歌えなかったことじゃない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.688716459,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_09_03/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_sigh-01.m4a",
      "text": "未練があるとしたら、それは12月25日に……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.797294378,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "琴乃の誕生日に歌えなかったことだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.4000176506,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_09_03/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_hey-01.m4a",
      "text": "今年の12月25日も、もうすぐだね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.4480201878,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "だからなのかな、ついこの歌を口ずさんじゃった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.0304761652,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_09_03/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_laughter-05.m4a",
      "text": "幽霊が歌っても、琴乃に届くはずないのにね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.8654162246,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_09_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "そんなことないさ。クリスマスは奇跡が起こる日だ\n歌に込めた麻奈の想いは、きっと琴乃に届いているよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 139.0333540358,
      "sfxList": []
